          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"implementing-a-new-plot\">Implementing a new plot</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">We'll show you how to implement a new plot using the nxviz's layered API.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">As an example, we'll show you how the design process works\nfor the matrix plot.</span></span>"
          }
