          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h3 id=\"annotate-matrix-blocks\">Annotate matrix blocks</h3>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">We could also annotate the matrix blocks using the exact same logic.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Matrix blocks are defined as the blocks of nodes in the same group,\nso this only applies to graphs for which the nodes can be grouped together.</span></span>"
